item.description: Freelancer Theme Freelancer Theme is a one page freelancer portfolio based on the original Bootstrap theme by David Miller and on Jerome Lachaud’s Jekyll theme. This Hugo theme features several content sections, a responsive portfolio grid with hover effects, full page portfolio item modals and a contact form.
